ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
SubjectOrder Transferring from the Minister of Health to the Minister of the Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency the Control and Supervision of the portion of the federal public administration known as the Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency and Ordering the Minister of the Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency to Preside over the Agency
PrecisOrder (a) transferring to the Minister of the Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency from the Minister of Health the control and supervision of that portion of the federal public administration known as the Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency; and (b) ordering that the Minister of the Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency shall preside over the Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency; and effective July 15, 2013.
